data.description: This well maintained home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with NO mandatory HOA. The inviting 2-story foyer greets you access to a formal living room or flex space, a generous sized dining room, and half bath. The eat-in kitchen, laundry room, large living room, and 2 car garage completes the main level. Upstairs features 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The primary bedroom has a nice sized sitting area, double vanity, separate shower and tub with a walk-in closet. Book your appointment today. Home to be sold AS-IS.
